resources.string: In this committe we learn new technologies and work together as a team and This is a reason to increase self-study and teamwork skills

We believe that knowledge and technologies does not belong to a person or a group of people. We believe that knowledge and technologies must be open and available for everybody to study, contribute, modify and share. We provide workshops to develop skills dealing with open source software therein. Like Blender 3D and Linux Workshops. We also create artistic animations using free software. We help students create and manage open source projects using our website
